---
description: NAKIVO modules and addon roots for work under nakivo/
globs: nakivo/**/*
alwaysApply: false
---

**Addon roots**: `nakivo-server/odoo/addons`, `nakivo-server/addons`, `nakivooca/`, `base_addons/`, `nakivo/`

**Main custom modules**: `nakivo_sale`, `nakivo_helpdesk`, `nakivo_crm_kpi`, `nakivo_dashboard`, `nakivo_base_security`, `nakivo_queue_jobs`, `nakivo_partner_level_management`, `nakivo_payments_import`, `odoo_ai_assistance`, connector modules, and `web_*`

**Addon layout**: `__manifest__.py`, `__init__.py`, `models/`, `views/`, `data/`, `security/`, `wizard/`, `controllers/`, `static/src/`
